information: We have been a successful manufacturer of liquid egg products for over 30 years. Thanks to the increasing use of pasteurised fresh eggs in the food industry combined with our philosophy of always providing our customers the very best quality, we have become one of the leading manufacturers of egg products in Germany. The quality of our products, the flexibility in our production and delivery processes and not least the fair prices we apply have made the CEWO-Wortmann family business a byword for market leading bakeries, pasta producers and manufacturers of convenience products. Our suppliers include selected producers who distinguish themselves through reliability, freshness and quality. Our products are made almost exclusively from deep-litter, free-range or organic eggs. By operating our own lab, we can constantly analyse quality at every stage of production. We are certified IFS, Bio, KAT and Kosher.
